                     <interp inst="t18300527-185-person1536" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the prosecutor's wife; he went out at a quarter-past nine o'clock in the morning; the prisoner came and asked for a person named Adams; I told him where he lived - I did not know that the coat was taken till the officer brought it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I bought it of a man in the street for 15s.</p>
